ingredients: ramen noodles, miso paste, pork broth, egg, nori, corn
recipe_steps:
1. Cook ramen in miso-infused broth.
2. Top with boiled egg, corn, and nori.
3. Serve hot with sesame oil drizzle.

ingredients: pork, ginger, garlic, soy sauce, sesame oil, green onions
recipe_steps:
1. Marinate pork with soy sauce and ginger.
2. Stir-fry garlic and pork until browned.
3. Add green onions and cook briefly.
4. Serve with rice or noodles.

ingredients: chickpeas, parsley, onion, garlic, spices, pita bread
recipe_steps:
1. Blend chickpeas with herbs and spices.
2. Shape into balls and fry.
3. Serve in pita with tahini sauce.

ingredients: rice, mixed vegetables, yogurt, spices, saffron, mint
recipe_steps:
1. Cook vegetables with yogurt and spices.
2. Layer with rice and saffron.
3. Cook on low heat (dum).
4. Garnish with mint and fried onions.

ingredients: chickpeas, parsley, onion, garlic, spices, pita bread
recipe_steps:
1. Blend chickpeas with herbs and spices.
2. Shape into balls and fry.
3. Serve in pita with tahini sauce.

recipe_steps:

4. Serve with salsa or guacamole.
